metadata.recording_metadata_summary: This recording is from a middle-school participating in the PLUS tutoring program. This school is called Jefferson. Students in this school use Chromebooks to access Zoom and generally use the math software Moby Max. The teacher in the classroom is named Codding, although other teachers may be present. The tutor assigned to this classroom is named Suhyun Baik, although other tutors may be present.
